text: Karamaly-Buzat () is a rural locality (a village) in Buzatovsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 10 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 55 km from Sterlibashevo, 8 km from Buzat. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Karamaly-Buzat
